  <title>Getting started</title>
  
  <p>This page describes how to get started using <app>PoProofRead</app>.</p>

  <section id="opening">
    <title>Opening the podiff-file</title>
    <p>First download the file you wish to work with,
    e.g. "<file>example.podiff</file>". There are now three different
    ways that you open the file:</p>
    <list>
      <item><p>Start <app>PoProofRead</app> and use the open file
      dialog (Ctrl-o)</p></item>
      <item><p>Right click the "<file>example.podiff</file>" file in
      your file browser and find <app>PoProofRead</app> among the
      applications in the "Open with"-menu</p></item>
      <item><p>Start <app>PoProofRead</app> from the terminal and
      supply the file as a argument e.g: <cmd>poproofread-gtk
      example.podiff</cmd></p></item>
    </list>
  </section>
